    <release version="1.0.0" date="2026-02-08" type="stable">
      <description>
        <p>Kuro 1.0.0 is a major milestone, reimagining the game for the modern GNOME ecosystem.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Modern Foundation: Complete rewrite using GTK4 and Libadwaita for a fluid, adaptive UI.</li>
          <li>Pause Overlay: New centered pause screen to prevent peeking while taking a break.</li>
          <li>Keyboard Navigation: Full support for playing with Arrow keys, WASD, or HJKL.</li>
          <li>Auto Theme: Seamlessly adapts to your system's light or dark style.</li>
          <li>Enhanced Gameplay: Improved Undo/Redo stack and board generation.</li>
          <li>New Identity: Rebranded from Hitori to Kuro with fresh iconography and metadata.</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
